_sText:
cs_mitsumedori is a port of the cs_mitsumedori map from the Counter-Strike: Global Offensive game.

- Counter-Terrorists: Escort hostage safely to to the drop ships. 

- Terrorists: Prevent Counter-Terrorist from rescuing the hostage.

--- 

- Beautiful map made in Asian style. 

- In this port of the map, I change the lighting a little, and change the skybox.

- Injoy
